# **A Note on Sustainability**

LCES was built in isolation — the way most pro se fights are fought.

But justice work lasts longer when it’s shared. Whether that’s connecting with others navigating similar terrain, or having a neutral professional space to process the pressure, support isn’t a weakness — it’s infrastructure.